flowchart LR
    subgraph Inputs["Input"]
        Stake[Stakeholder<br/>Requirements]
    end

    subgraph PB["Backlog Refinement"]
        Backlog[(Product<br/>Backlog)]
    end

    subgraph Sprint["Sprint (1-4 minggu)"]
        direction TB
        Plan[Sprint Planning<br/>What & How]
        SBacklog[(Sprint<br/>Backlog)]
        Daily[Daily Scrum<br/>15 menit]
        Work[Development<br/>Work]
        Inc[(Increment<br/>Potentially Shippable)]
        Review[Sprint Review<br/>Demo Inspect]
        Retro[Retrospective<br/>Adapt Process]

        Plan --> SBacklog
        SBacklog --> Daily
        Daily --> Work
        Work --> Daily
        Work --> Inc
        Inc --> Review
        Review --> Retro
    end

    Stake -->|requirements| Backlog
    Backlog -->|prioritized<br/>items| Plan
    Retro -->|process<br/>improvements| Plan
    Retro -.->|next sprint| Plan
    Inc -->|deliver| Stake

    classDef input fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b
    classDef backlog fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#ec4899
    classDef event fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6
    classDef artifact fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#10b981

    class Stake input
    class Backlog,SBacklog backlog
    class Plan,Daily,Work,Review,Retro event
    class Inc artifact
